  [ Kamal Mostafa ]

  * Release Tracking Bug
    - LP: #1597902

  [ Ubuntu: 4.4.0-30.49 ]

  * FCP devices are not detected correctly nor deterministically (LP: #1567602)
    - scsi_dh_alua: Disable ALUA handling for non-disk devices
    - scsi_dh_alua: Use vpd_pg83 information
